docs.text: darren ( jason biggs ) , wayne ( steve zahn ) , and j . d . ( jack black ) have been best friends since the fifth grade .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: like the three musketeers , they've been together through thick and thin .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: but , when darren meets an attractive , but cold-blooded and manipulative , psychiatrist , judith ( amanda peet ) , the long time friendship is placed in danger .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: it's up to wayne and j . d . to rescue their best friend in " saving silverman . "
docs.label: negative

docs.text: " silverman " has its heart in the right place , but the story , by newcomers hank nelken and greg depaul , is too lightweight to sustain the tale of the battle for darren's soul .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: based on their experience of a friend making a major marital mistake , the story is centered on the three , life long amigos .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: when wayne introduces darren to judith , he doesn't realize that he has opened a pandora's box of disaster for himself and j . d . judith was once in a relationship where her boyfriend was the dominant figure until he died in a kick boxing match .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: since then , she has sought a new mate - someone she can boss around and mold into her own vision .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: enter darren silverman .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: once they realize the magnitude of their error in judgement , wayne and j . d . try everything they can , including threats and bribery , to get judith to free darren .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: nothing works until the duo come up with a plan - kidnap judith and get darren back together with the girl he called his one and only , pretty sandy perkus ( amanda detmer ) .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: the only problem here is that sandy is about to take her vows to become a nun .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: things spiral out of control as judith repeatedly attempts to escape while wayne and j . d . play cupid .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: the boys even bring their idol , neil diamond , into the picture to help resolve things .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: thinking about it , this is a real mishmash of contrivance and coincidence that is held together solely by the comedic efforts of steve zahn and jack black .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: the pair is able to elicit the film's only laughs with their goofy antics and child-like behavior .

docs.text: they are relegated to providing slapstick guy humor and the two are more than equal to the task .
